Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These stewed potatoes are really tasty!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.38,0:03:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, thank you. Eat as much as you want.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.76,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Ruuko, c'mon and eat some more!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.72,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.39,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for Yuzuki-san not to go home?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! That bath felt really good!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.40,0:03:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuffed myself with food and took a hot bath. Now I'm Enercharged!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.53,0:03:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Orichalcum, Attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.20,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That tickles, Y-Yuzuki-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.29,0:03:49.58,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,Take this, and that!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I said some horrible things to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what you're thinking, Ruuko!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.81,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what she's thinking...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.69,0:04:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine! Don't worry about it.\NIt doesn't bother me one bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.78,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.03,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In my battle against Akira...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to lose no matter what.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,have someone that I like.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.21,0:04:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But he'll never return my feelings...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.25,0:04:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you know? I mean, you are cute and all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it just won't happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.01,0:04:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}shouldn't{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.56,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But if my wish came true,\NI could like him just like anyone else...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.86,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. Could it be that you like Kazu—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it already!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it feels like to be in love.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it gets you really excited, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.77,0:05:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Excited? Excited in battle! Tama!
