Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? She went home already?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like, a while ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.99,0:06:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-san was writing about decks and battle progression.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to try to do it, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.95,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea. You can look at your deck objectively like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitoe-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran away...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to be friends with you, Ruuko-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.28,0:07:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be your friend...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki-san, you too!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Being her friend? Sure, why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Two friends at once?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.35,0:07:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,WIXOSS is so wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.14,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.81,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was battling Akira-san, it was so painful that I thought I was going to break.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know that feeling.{iktfb}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Selector battles are painful.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.20,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was natural since\Nyou're trying to attain your wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.95,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But while I was battling Ruuko-san,\NI enjoyed it from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.34,0:08:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.42,0:08:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's play a game of WIXOSS to celebrate our friendship.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.38,0:08:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.18,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, if Selectors battle each other,\Nsomeone's wish will...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.97,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Hanayo-san and the others aren't in our decks, we can just hold regular card battles.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, you three wait here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have fun, Hitoe.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.95,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn end.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn now, Hitoe-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.92,0:08:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.30,0:08:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We did rock-paper-scissors, remember? You're next.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.92,0:08:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.76,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll summon Baromet.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.80,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uhm...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.93,0:09:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Baromet's power is 7000, so won't it get banished by Yuzuki-san's LRIG's ability after it grows?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.94,0:09:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruuko! Stop saying stuff from the sidelines!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.99,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama wants to join!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama and Ruuko are really alike.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Hitoe's wish already came true.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't need to battle anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.05,0:09:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means you...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that, Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.90,0:09:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.52,0:09:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry. I called you by name.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling you by name already too, y'know?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.66,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel your friendship, it's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.16,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you call us by name too, Hitoe-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.41,0:10:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you "Hitoe," too.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.71,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay... Then, R-Ruuko, Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.63,0:10:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That feels so weird!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.47,0:10:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so weird!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Hitoe smile like that before.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I wasn't her LRIG.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not allowed to say that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama likes Ruu!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.11,0:10:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I like Ruu. Tama likes being Ruu's LRIG!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.11,0:10:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Tama and Ruuko are friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.91,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanayo, Tama is...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.46,0:10:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she doesn't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm next!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like WIXOSS, don't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I really, really like it!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! At the entrance gate!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.15,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Akira is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the model?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.16,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww... Ruu-Ruu went home already?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.45,0:11:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so mean, breaking a promise like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.42,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira knows Kominato-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Kominato?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare she make Akira sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.59,0:11:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu-Ruu didn't do anything bad.\NI'll come back again...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I do if she goes home early again?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.52,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if someone would let Akira know about Ruu-Ruu...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira's so gallant!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! I'll let you know for sure!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you know, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you! Well, I have a shoot I need to go to, so see you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go home...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be running from Kazuki forever, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.14,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Akira came to our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too strong, Ruuko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then! Milk tea for me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.20,0:12:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have some sweet bean soup.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.12,0:12:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right. I come back and all of a sudden I'm the errand boy, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.45,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on already!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.50,0:12:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruuko, you look happier now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.50,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Ruu-chan is going to battle me. Whoever loses has to clean the bath.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But Grandma, you're too good!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.51,0:13:11.56,Default,,0,0,0, [redundant tags],{\i1}I wish we could battle and have fun like this all the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.94,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.90,0:13:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Battling with Tama is a lot more fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.98,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not just for play.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in a battlefield.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Battles against Selectors.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.37,0:13:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But those are battles for everyone's wishes.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.75,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any wishes,\Nso I shouldn't get in their way.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.01,0:13:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu-chan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.17,0:13:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry! It's my turn, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.06,0:13:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-san is looking for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.19,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.98,0:13:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She really wants to battle you, Ruuko-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.81,0:14:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she's so persistent!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.02,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't have any wishes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.32,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I lose to Akira-san,\Nit won't mean much...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you, so don't you worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.42,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll probably be some bad rumors\Nabout you, but just try to ignore them.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's trying to disturb you as much as she can.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have any other friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.22,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu-Ruu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ruu-Ruu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.10,0:14:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been waiting for you.\NLet's go to class.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.36,0:14:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. I just got a message from Aki-lucky.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.11,0:14:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She invited us to come down to the photo studio with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said she'd show us around the studio if we went together.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.91,Default, [time gap 170ms],0,0,0,,We might even get to meet Iona—
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.91,0:14:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go. We have something to do after school.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.33,0:15:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not invited, so shut it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.25,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.13,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Ruu-Ruu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.44,0:15:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruuko...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.84,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"There is no stronger bond of friendship than a mutual enemy..."
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that will be it for today. The remainder...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.43,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruuko, let's go home!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.98,0:15:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.73,0:15:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Can students from other classes please refrain from entering?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.94,0:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving anyways!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Ruuko!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.07,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Coming...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.20,0:15:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey girls, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.20,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it, Scrub-face!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Scrub-face?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.59,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!\NSend a message to everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.43,0:15:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way, gramps!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruuko, this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're {\i1}really{\i0} persistent!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.24,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Yuzuki. I'll just go and battle her.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.71,0:16:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember how I said that I didn't know what you were thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.26,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I do know one thing now for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.97,0:16:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That you really like having WIXOSS battles.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Battling Akira is going to be really painful.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.98,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Battling her may make you hate WIXOSS.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that to happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.08,0:17:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they go this way?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The freshmen said they saw them.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.38,0:17:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.13,0:17:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw them outside, so you stay put here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.71,0:17:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.22,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll catch you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.27,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.61,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki must be really worried about me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.29,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can tell her...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.09,0:17:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That even if I'm hurt or pained...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I {\i0}want{\i1} to battle Akira-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.34,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu and Tama are same!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to battle Akira!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tama is... scary...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.36,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm... like Tama.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what Ruuko is thinking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.16,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's scary.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuzu—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruu-Ruu...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.31,0:18:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.15,0:18:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We've brought her!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.77,0:18:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No ways! Seriously? Shucks, thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything for Aki-lucky!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.36,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awesome! Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.12,0:19:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Ruu-Ruu, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what about us?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a photo shoot, so leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Weren't you gonna show us around the studio?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.92,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no place for uglies like yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.38,0:19:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bother me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will get in our way here.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's start our battle.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.12,Default,,0,0,0, [redundant tags],{\i1}A battle against Akira-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.04,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if you're going to battle, let me in too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.55,0:20:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Stop trying to take my prey!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind facing you either.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.72,0:20:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you want to battle me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you scared of me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You're up next.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.78,0:20:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, uh, just a moment. I'm...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.32,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, just wait a...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.24,0:20:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hurry up! Everyone is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you thanking me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.22,0:20:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to battle, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.51,0:20:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to battle Akira.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.52,0:20:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.93,0:20:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone would have been fine so long as you could play WIXOSS.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to play for real, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.20,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,do it with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.92,0:21:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,don't have any wishes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.43,0:21:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For someone without a wish to participate as a WIXOSS Selector is...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,blasphemy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't allowed.
